<i>Right from the start,</i>
<i>been friends forever</i>

39:19.200 --> 39:23.205
<i>Somehow we're meant to be together</i>

39:23.960 --> 39:28.999
<i>I feel like you've shown me</i>
<i>how to find my way home</i>

