Thank you, Kenai.

41:00.200 --> 41:02.039
<i>Home, home</i>

41:02.040 --> 41:06.648
<i>Feels just like home</i>

41:19.760 --> 41:23.207
Hey, smallish bear.
So where's big bear, eh?

41:23.880 --> 41:25.325
With Nita.

41:26.320 --> 41:30.609
He never has time for me any more.
He's too busy helping her.

41:31.080 --> 41:34.004
Shee! Boy, do I know how you feel.

41:34.080 --> 41:38.369
My own brother gave me the heave-ho,
eh, all for a babe.

41:38.760 --> 41:41.240
Actually, two really, really hot babes.

41:42.200 --> 41:44.771
Better watch your brother
doesn't walk out on you, eh.

41:46.920 --> 41:48.410
He wouldn't do that.

41:49.240 --> 41:51.004
I said the same thing, eh,

41:51.080 --> 41:53.321
but get a load of Moose-anova
over there.

41:53.600 --> 41:56.809
Shall I compare thee to a summer's dew?

41:56.880 --> 41:58.439
Did you just make that up?

41:58.440 --> 41:59.930
- Beauty, eh.
- He's such a poet.

42:02.760 --> 42:05.411
Yeah, I guess I'll see you around, little bear.

42:28.120 --> 42:30.771
- You had a whole clumpful.
- Oh, you're making that up.

42:30.840 --> 42:33.730
All I know is I had all my fur
when we went into the river,

42:33.800 --> 42:35.370
and two handfuls were missing when we came out.

42:35.600 --> 42:37.799
- Well, maybe you're just going bald.
- What?

42:37.800 --> 42:40.963
You know, it does look
really thin right through here.

42:41.240 --> 42:43.083
Yeah, very funny.

42:44.000 --> 42:46.519
This is the most fun I've had
since we were kids.

42:48.320 --> 42:50.368
Fun but cold.

42:50.440 --> 42:52.727
On a night like this, it's good to be a bear.

42:53.040 --> 42:54.451
I bet.

43:03.320 --> 43:06.005
So, Hokani Falls.

43:07.560 --> 43:10.211
I guess we'll make it there in time, huh?

43:11.040 --> 43:12.326
I guess.

43:13.080 --> 43:15.970
A lot sure has changed
since the last time we were there.

43:16.840 --> 43:18.171
No kidding.

43:20.000 --> 43:23.049
Do you ever miss being human?

43:23.680 --> 43:30.165
I mean, have you ever thought about
changing back?

43:34.880 --> 43:36.325
Yeah, I've...

43:37.120 --> 43:38.879
I've thought about it.

43:38.880 --> 43:40.006
I knew it.

43:41.880 --> 43:42.927
Koda.

43:44.600 --> 43:45.886
You're going back with her.

43:46.000 --> 43:47.411
Koda, wait. Koda, wait!

43:56.840 --> 43:57.887
Koda!

44:03.360 --> 44:05.010
Koda, answer me!

44:23.800 --> 44:24.881
Koda!

44:41.760 --> 44:43.046
Hello?

44:46.040 --> 44:48.691
Koda? Are you in here?

44:57.400 --> 44:58.890
Where are you?

44:59.880 --> 45:01.370
Koda?

45:04.360 --> 45:05.407
Koda?

45:05.880 --> 45:07.245
Go away.

45:07.800 --> 45:12.203
Koda, Kenai's worried sick about you.
Come on, I'll take you to him.

45:12.440 --> 45:14.522
No! I said go away!

45:17.400 --> 45:20.688
Koda, please keep your voice down.
It's not safe.

45:20.760 --> 45:23.001
I don't care. Just leave me alone.

45:26.360 --> 45:27.566
No, Nita!

45:29.560 --> 45:31.483
We're gonna be all right, but we've got to go.

45:32.800 --> 45:33.801
Now!

45:36.320 --> 45:39.483
Run! Run! Run! Faster!

45:43.320 --> 45:44.765
We're gonna make it.

45:46.800 --> 45:48.802
- Nita!
- Take my hand.

45:59.000 --> 46:00.081
Don't move.

46:09.320 --> 46:10.367
Koda!

46:11.640 --> 46:12.846
Hang on!

46:13.680 --> 46:14.681
Nita!

46:14.800 --> 46:15.847
Don't let go!

46:19.640 --> 46:21.927
- Koda, hold on!
- I am!

46:32.440 --> 46:33.680
Koda.

46:48.040 --> 46:51.840
Koda, what would I have done
if anything happened to you?

46:52.800 --> 46:57.681
You're gonna leave me.
You said you missed being one of them.

47:08.600 --> 47:11.001
You're going back with her, aren't you?

47:12.720 --> 47:14.290
I do miss things,

47:15.800 --> 47:17.245
but you're my brother.

47:18.040 --> 47:19.929
I'll never leave you.

47:20.360 --> 47:23.091
Ah. Not ever.

47:58.520 --> 48:00.959
Ah, this show's giving me the munchies, eh.

48:00.960 --> 48:03.327
Hey, little brother,
how about you get us some twigs, eh?

48:03.440 --> 48:05.647
Okay.

48:06.960 --> 48:08.325
Are you crying?

48:09.080 --> 48:12.766
No. I mean, well, yeah, but so what, eh?

48:12.960 --> 48:15.327
These lights are so beautiful, eh, I...

48:16.880 --> 48:18.803
Oh, he's sensitive.

48:19.160 --> 48:20.764
A moose with depth?

48:21.240 --> 48:22.969
It's beauty, eh.

48:23.480 --> 48:24.606
What?

48:24.680 --> 48:26.359
He's a cute one, isn't he?

48:26.360 --> 48:28.647
Hey, I can be sensitive, too, eh.

48:29.000 --> 48:30.650
Ooh, I like your hooves.

48:30.760 --> 48:31.839
Really?

48:31.840 --> 48:35.765
Yeah, and I'm a hoof man.
Yours are nice and shiny.

48:37.760 --> 48:40.331
Hoof man? Why didn't I think of that?

49:21.200 --> 49:22.929
Is this the equinox?

49:23.920 --> 49:26.571
Yeah, Koda, this is it.

49:57.560 --> 49:59.449
My mom is up there somewhere.

50:00.360 --> 50:01.850
My mom, too.

50:02.640 --> 50:05.007
Do you miss yours?

50:07.240 --> 50:08.446
Yes.

50:09.480 --> 50:13.610
But you don't need to wait for the lights
to find her, Koda.

50:14.680 --> 50:16.444
She's always with you.

50:17.320 --> 50:18.731
In here.

50:19.840 --> 50:25.324
Once you love someone,
they stay in your heart forever.

50:33.960 --> 50:35.610
It's time.

51:22.920 --> 51:25.924
Koda, you be good, okay?

51:27.600 --> 51:29.602
You're such a sweet little cub.

51:34.280 --> 51:36.886
Oh, the spell.

51:51.000 --> 51:52.365
Goodbye.

52:08.120 --> 52:10.521
<i>If you hear a voice</i>

52:11.160 --> 52:13.845
<i>In the middle of the night</i>

52:14.720 --> 52:17.041
<i>Saying it'll be all right</i>

52:18.040 --> 52:20.566
<i>It will be me</i>

52:21.280 --> 52:23.806
<i>If you feel a hand</i>

52:24.520 --> 52:27.091
<i>Guiding you along</i>

52:27.720 --> 52:30.530
<i>When the path seems wrong</i>

52:31.160 --> 52:33.640
<i>It will be me</i>

52:34.360 --> 52:37.250
<i>There is no mountain</i>

52:37.520 --> 52:40.171
<i>That I can't climb</i>

52:40.800 --> 52:46.648
<i>For you, I'd swim through</i>
<i>the rivers of time</i>

52:47.240 --> 52:53.009
<i>As you go your way and I go mine</i>

52:53.760 --> 52:56.604
<i>Our light will shine</i>

52:56.920 --> 53:01.369
<i>And it will be me</i>

53:03.520 --> 53:08.003
<i>It will be me</i>

53:09.800 --> 53:15.091
<i>It will be me</i>

53:29.480 --> 53:33.804
Kenai, did you give Nita the amulet
because you loved her?

53:37.440 --> 53:39.204
It was a long time ago.

53:39.800 --> 53:42.963
But she's still with you in here.

53:43.760 --> 53:45.205
I can tell.

53:45.440 --> 53:48.649
Ah, Koda, it doesn't matter.

53:49.960 --> 53:53.681
Well, if you do love her,
shouldn't you tell her?

53:54.400 --> 53:57.404
It's a little more complicated than that.

53:58.800 --> 54:01.690
Anyway, it's over.

54:02.960 --> 54:06.931
Hey, I promised you we'd be the
first two bears to Crowberry Ridge.

54:07.600 --> 54:09.443
Pinkie swear, remember?

54:10.240 --> 54:13.722
How about first thing in the morning,
we rustle up some more berries?

54:13.800 --> 54:15.006
Sound good?

54:40.640 --> 54:43.644
Mom, Kenai's so sad.

54:45.040 --> 54:46.849
It's all because of me.

54:48.880 --> 54:50.882
I'll be okay on my own.

54:51.520 --> 54:55.445
Tell the spirits to change Kenai back
so he can be happy.

55:12.560 --> 55:14.403
- Jeez, he's really out, eh.
- Yeah.

55:14.404 --> 55:16.439
Maybe we should throw some water on his face.

55:16.440 --> 55:18.727
Why don't you just stand
there drooling, eh? That should do it.

55:18.800 --> 55:19.847
Trample off.

55:19.960 --> 55:21.928
Oh, wait. Hey, I think I saw him move.

55:24.400 --> 55:26.562
Rise and shine, bear boy!

55:26.680 --> 55:28.728
Yeah, not time to hydroplane yet, eh.

55:28.880 --> 55:31.167
- It's hibernate, you hoofer.
- That's what I said.

55:31.400 --> 55:33.243
Hey, we saw smallish bear last night.

55:33.440 --> 55:36.239
Yeah, we tried to stop him, eh,
but he wouldn't listen to us.

55:36.240 --> 55:37.919
What? Where was he going?

55:37.920 --> 55:39.279
Uh... Oh.

55:39.280 --> 55:40.691
To get Nita, eh.

55:40.760 --> 55:42.649
He said he was gonna bring her back for you.

55:42.650 --> 55:45.644
Bring her back? No, no.

55:45.840 --> 55:48.207
If he steps foot in the village,
the hunters will get him.

55:49.920 --> 55:51.445
Oh, gee.

55:54.360 --> 55:55.799
Almost there.

55:55.800 --> 55:59.850
And now for the final touch,
a beautiful bead necklace.

55:59.920 --> 56:02.321
Oh, no, you don't. Not this time.

56:02.400 --> 56:04.279
This is much more appropriate.

56:04.280 --> 56:06.521
Yeah, and that doesn't match
anything she's wearing.

56:06.600 --> 56:08.602
And what makes you think those beads do?

56:09.000 --> 56:11.287
Nita, what would make you happy?

56:17.000 --> 56:18.650
Once again, we are ready.

56:20.200 --> 56:21.645
Are you, my daughter?

56:23.160 --> 56:24.321
Yes, Father.

56:30.280 --> 56:34.080
I would expect a bride
to be smiling on her wedding day.

56:35.320 --> 56:36.890
Is there something wrong?

56:38.840 --> 56:42.003
Daddy, I'm so confused.

56:44.920 --> 56:48.481
I thought that when I burned the amulet,
the bond would be broken,

56:51.240 --> 56:53.208
but in my heart, I...

56:56.720 --> 56:58.449
I'm sorry, Daddy.

57:00.240 --> 57:02.049
I can't marry Atka.

57:07.520 --> 57:08.567
Nita...

57:08.640 --> 57:11.120
A bear! There's a bear in the village!

57:11.920 --> 57:13.285
It's a bear.

57:13.560 --> 57:16.211
Koda? Wait! Wait, don't hurt him.

57:17.000 --> 57:18.286
No, our fish!

57:19.080 --> 57:20.127
I got him!

57:20.680 --> 57:22.011
We've got him now!

57:22.760 --> 57:25.650
- Look, he's up in the tree!
- There he is. Get him!

57:26.120 --> 57:27.239
Don't!

57:27.240 --> 57:28.605
Don't! Please stop!

57:33.720 --> 57:35.449
Look out, here he comes!

57:38.880 --> 57:40.245
- Get your spears!
- Come on!

57:40.360 --> 57:42.044
- Let's go after him.
- Atka, no!

57:43.560 --> 57:45.767
- Leave him alone.
- Get him!

57:51.160 --> 57:52.764
Oh, no. Run!

57:52.880 --> 57:54.006
This way.

57:55.920 --> 57:57.331
After them!

57:58.040 --> 57:59.405
Nita, are you hurt?

57:59.560 --> 58:00.891
I have to stop them.

58:03.720 --> 58:06.007
There he is! Let's get him!

58:10.440 --> 58:11.566
Follow me!

58:14.000 --> 58:16.446
Rock! Look out! Get out of the way!

58:20.200 --> 58:21.361
Stay low.

58:23.240 --> 58:24.241
Kenai!

58:32.920 --> 58:34.081
Hmm...

58:36.560 --> 58:38.847
There you are. Got you!

58:49.120 --> 58:50.121
Nice move, eh.

58:50.200 --> 58:52.009
Gee, eh.

58:52.080 --> 58:54.731
Oh! Our heroes.

58:56.680 --> 58:57.806
Beauty, eh.

58:57.880 --> 59:00.281
Come on! We have to find Kenai.

59:23.440 --> 59:25.283
Aah!

59:32.480 --> 59:33.720
Kenai!

59:41.880 --> 59:43.325
No, don't!

59:50.000 --> 59:51.161
Kenai!

01:00:05.240 --> 01:00:06.526
How could you?

01:00:07.200 --> 01:00:09.123
- What?
- He was my friend.

01:00:20.840 --> 01:00:22.046
Kenai?

01:00:56.560 --> 01:01:00.645
I can't... I don't understand. I'm sorry.

01:01:19.080 --> 01:01:20.650
I love you, too.

01:01:40.160 --> 01:01:41.321
The spirits?

01:01:42.160 --> 01:01:45.243
Kenai, I can understand you.

01:01:46.320 --> 01:01:49.130
I asked the spirits to turn you back into a man.

01:01:49.800 --> 01:01:51.450
- What?
- So you could be with Nita.

01:01:52.640 --> 01:01:53.641
No, Koda.

01:01:53.960 --> 01:01:57.601
It's okay.
I just want you to be happy again.

01:02:00.200 --> 01:02:03.124
Nita, I can't.

01:02:10.000 --> 01:02:11.411
But I can.

01:02:14.160 --> 01:02:17.562
Am I the only one that hears
these bears speaking?

01:02:17.640 --> 01:02:20.325
- Yeah, that's beauty, eh.
- How's it going, eh?

01:02:20.880 --> 01:02:22.006
Father.

01:02:26.520 --> 01:02:28.010
Is this what you want?

01:02:29.880 --> 01:02:31.644
Will this make you happy?

01:02:35.920 --> 01:02:37.809
You are my daughter

01:02:37.880 --> 01:02:40.724
and I will love you no matter what you choose.

01:03:46.840 --> 01:03:47.959
Nita?

01:03:53.680 --> 01:03:55.170
How do I look?

01:03:55.400 --> 01:03:58.882
Like a bear, except they gave you antlers.

01:03:59.120 --> 01:04:00.326
What?

01:04:00.600 --> 01:04:02.125
Gotcha!

01:04:21.280 --> 01:04:23.123
<i>Life is simple and clear</i>

01:04:23.680 --> 01:04:25.728
<i>When you make the right choice</i>

01:04:25.880 --> 01:04:27.689
<i>It's truth that you hear</i>

01:04:27.840 --> 01:04:30.320
<i>When you find your own voice</i>

01:04:30.400 --> 01:04:34.086
<i>Oh, my brothers and sisters, believe</i>

01:04:34.200 --> 01:04:37.966
<i>You are just what you are meant to be</i>

01:04:38.040 --> 01:04:41.408
<i>Oh, great spirits</i>

01:04:41.560 --> 01:04:46.805
<i>Hear my voice today</i>

01:04:46.880 --> 01:04:49.690
- I love happy endings, eh.
- I love happy endings, too.

01:04:49.800 --> 01:04:51.564
And happy beginnings.

01:04:52.120 --> 01:04:53.485
- Beauty, eh.
- Beauty.

01:04:55.840 --> 01:04:57.330
Ow!

01:05:01.440 --> 01:05:04.444
<i>Look all around you</i>

01:05:05.000 --> 01:05:07.731
<i>Welcome, magic</i>

01:05:08.240 --> 01:05:10.846
<i>Welcome, sweet sun ray</i>

01:05:10.920 --> 01:05:13.048
<i>Welcome, my sweet sun ray</i>

01:05:13.120 --> 01:05:14.565
<i>Love is no secret</i>

01:05:14.840 --> 01:05:17.002
<i>Look all around you</i>

01:05:17.120 --> 01:05:20.249
<i>Welcome to this day</i>

01:05:21.400 --> 01:05:23.679
<i>Welcome, magic</i>

01:05:23.680 --> 01:05:25.808
<i>Love is no secret</i>

01:05:25.880 --> 01:05:27.999
<i>Look all around you</i>

01:05:28.000 --> 01:05:31.641
<i>Welcome to this day</i>

01:05:55.200 --> 01:05:57.519
<i>Learning how to smile again</i>

01:05:57.520 --> 01:05:59.522
<i>Free to show my heart</i>

01:05:59.880 --> 01:06:04.249
<i>Knowing I can face the things</i>
<i>that used to seem too hard</i>

01:06:04.640 --> 01:06:06.881
<i>I look inside your eyes and see</i>

01:06:07.000 --> 01:06:08.879
<i>A different part of me</i>

01:06:08.880 --> 01:06:11.611
<i>What I didn't know I want in life</i>

01:06:11.680 --> 01:06:13.921
<i>You're everything I need</i>

01:06:14.440 --> 01:06:18.559
<i>So many things I've been missin'</i>
<i>and not watchin'</i>

01:06:18.560 --> 01:06:21.962
<i>But that was all in the past</i>

01:06:22.080 --> 01:06:26.802
<i>Now I realise</i>
<i>there's so much more to learn</i>

01:06:26.880 --> 01:06:29.119
